1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:18,410 --> 00:01:25,360
[Flight to you]

3
00:01:28,289 --> 00:01:30,720
[Episode 11]

4
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,410
Brother Qiao, Cheng, you are off work.

5
00:01:35,410 --> 00:01:35,970
Bye.

6
00:01:36,090 --> 00:01:36,490
Bye.

7
00:01:36,509 --> 00:01:37,150
Okay, bye.

8
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:38,720
Cheng,

9
00:01:39,390 --> 00:01:40,960
you look very happy today.

10
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:42,870
Did something good happen?

11
00:01:43,190 --> 00:01:43,680
Did I?

12
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,410
You go first. See you tomorrow.

13
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:51,720
Bye.

14
00:01:51,970 --> 00:01:52,470
Bye.

15
00:01:55,370 --> 00:01:56,039
Hello.

16
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,920
Are you Ms. Cheng?

17
00:01:58,250 --> 00:01:59,180
Yes, who are you?

18
00:01:59,750 --> 00:02:01,170
I'm from Jia's Real Estate.

19
00:02:01,170 --> 00:02:02,680
You bought that house here.

20
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,610
Do you remember?

21
00:02:04,270 --> 00:02:05,070
Yes.

22
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,080
What's wrong?

23
00:02:06,970 --> 00:02:08,560
A buyer is interested in your house.

24
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,690
He wants to discuss the price with you.

25
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:11,570
What?

26
00:02:11,870 --> 00:02:13,410
Didn't you sell your house?

27
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,200
Today, a client

28
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,540
went to check out the house.

29
00:02:16,540 --> 00:02:17,340
Wait a minute.

30
00:02:18,090 --> 00:02:19,490
When did I sell it?

31
00:02:20,890 --> 00:02:23,290
Your mother came to our company and sold it.

32
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:25,360
She's been on the phone.

33
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:26,829
We couldn't reach her,

34
00:02:26,829 --> 00:02:28,960
so we decided to contact you directly.

35
00:02:37,660 --> 00:02:38,829
The three of us

36
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,760
haven't eaten together for a long time.

37
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,440
Apply this to make you look younger.

38
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,280
What's wrong?

39
00:02:46,890 --> 00:02:48,230
I look old if I don't apply it, right?

40
00:02:48,230 --> 00:02:50,120
Don't say that. I'm praising you.

41
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,000
Look at your daughter.

42
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,829
What's wrong with her today,

43
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,510
buying me dinner?

44
00:02:56,570 --> 00:02:58,730
It's nice for our daughter to treat us.

45
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,370
But you say it differently.

46
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,320
Don't listen if you don't like it.

47
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:02,980
I do.

48
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,870
I've heard it for half of my life. I'm used to it.

49
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:07,930
Hurry up. Xiaoxiao will be back soon.

50
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:14,580
Who asked you to sell my house?

51
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,470
What house?

52
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,079
My house

53
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:21,480
was earned by myself.

54
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:23,500
You don't have a penny in it.

55
00:03:23,510 --> 00:03:25,710
Why did you put my house on the platform?

56
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:26,329
Why?

57
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:28,320
Because I'm your mother.

58
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,410
You're a lawyer.

59
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,680
You should know

60
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:31,690
even if you're a mother,

61
00:03:31,690 --> 00:03:33,720
you can't touch your children's property at will

62
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,760
I can sue you.

63
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:36,280
Fine, go ahead.

64
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:38,890
You don't live in such a big house in Qingdao.

65
00:03:38,890 --> 00:03:39,840
Why do you have to

66
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:41,640
buy this shabby and small house here?

67
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:42,920
I'm telling you, sell it now.

68
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:43,600
Come back with me.

69
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,240
I left Qingdao

70
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,650
to stay away from you.

71
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:47,240
So even if I live on the street,

72
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,200
I won’t go back.

73
00:03:48,579 --> 00:03:49,240
Cheng Xiao.

74
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:56,050
OK.

75
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,840
Xiaoxiao.

76
00:04:00,230 --> 00:04:01,160
What's going on?

77
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:07,800
Listen.

78
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,760
I'll wait for you at the train station.

79
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,820
If you don't come,

80
00:04:11,010 --> 00:04:12,040
you'll be like her.

81
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,700
Don't ever go back to Qingdao.

82
00:04:16,170 --> 00:04:18,149
Xiaoyun, there's no car now.

83
00:04:18,170 --> 00:04:19,230
Won't I take a taxi?

84
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:21,190
I mean the train.

85
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:51,060
[Renovation Contract]

86
00:05:23,130 --> 00:05:23,770
Xiaoxiao,

87
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:27,740
I want to apologize to you for mum today.

88
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:31,540
She shouldn't have gone through your stuff.

89
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:34,790
Sorry, dad.

90
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:39,000
I didn't tell you that I bought a house.

91
00:05:39,940 --> 00:05:40,870
I thought I could

92
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:41,920
give you a surprise

93
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,020
after renovating.

94
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,240
Invite you here

95
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,370
for staying a while.

96
00:05:48,030 --> 00:05:48,630
It's okay.

97
00:05:50,380 --> 00:05:51,980
When the renovation is done,

98
00:05:52,020 --> 00:05:53,220
I'll come for a visit.

99
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:55,480
I'll come alone.

100
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:56,200
Okay.

101
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:03,770
Don't be sad. Xiaoxiao.

102
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:05,900
Actually,

103
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,660
we should say sorry.

104
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:11,200
We shouldn't have come.

105
00:06:20,810 --> 00:06:21,800
I'm sorry, dad.

106
00:06:24,540 --> 00:06:25,810
Don't be sad.

107
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:34,790
Here.

108
00:06:35,380 --> 00:06:36,440
I'm not crying.

109
00:06:44,430 --> 00:06:45,960
There's no car at this hour.

110
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,860
Go find her.

111
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:50,960
Forget it.

112
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,700
We'll stay in a hotel

113
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,560
nearby the train station.

114
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,820
In case you fight again

115
00:06:56,909 --> 00:06:58,040
when she comes back.

116
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:07,890
Alright.

117
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:09,900
Xiaoxiao,

118
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,440
you must

119
00:07:12,650 --> 00:07:14,180
take good care of yourself.

120
00:07:15,930 --> 00:07:17,930
Don't bear everything by yourself.

121
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,050
You can tell me.

122
00:07:24,710 --> 00:07:25,510
Do you hear me?

123
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:32,850
Alright.

124
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:36,880
Come on.

125
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,900
Alright, stop crying.

126
00:07:40,909 --> 00:07:41,510
Don't cry.

127
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:04,600
[Staff room]

128
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,530
Are you busy?

129
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:12,280
Cheng, I'm done.

130
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:13,170
Take your time.

131
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:32,880
Ms. Cheng,

132
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:35,080
do you still need to sell the house?

133
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,440
Ms. Cheng.

134
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,730
Just hang it.

135
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,820
Let's wait and see who bids with the higher price.

136
00:08:45,820 --> 00:08:46,820
We can talk later.

137
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,930
Should I contact Auntie Fang

138
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:51,010
or contact you if there are any updates?

139
00:08:51,010 --> 00:08:52,320
My name is on the deed.

140
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:53,880
I'm the one who is responsible for it.

141
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:54,420
Okay.

142
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,820
I'll contact you if there's any news.

143
00:09:02,510 --> 00:09:03,170
Cheng Xiao.

144
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:08,660
Just this much?

145
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,290
I'm on a diet.

146
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:17,930
Why can't I reach your phone all the time?

147
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:26,630
Don't think I don't know you blocked me.

148
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:28,540
Really?

149
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,740
Let me see.

150
00:09:33,570 --> 00:09:36,770
Maybe I accidentally pressed the wrong button last time.

151
00:09:39,690 --> 00:09:40,840
Okay, it's fine now.

152
00:09:43,870 --> 00:09:44,930
I’m here to tell you

153
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:48,050
you can return to the Flight Department.

154
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:50,160
Really?

155
00:09:53,770 --> 00:09:54,640
You know what?

156
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:56,140
When I was transferred to the Ground Handling Department,

157
00:09:56,140 --> 00:09:57,880
my engine was about to fail.

158
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:01,410
You can make up for it, even if it's a double-engine failure.

159
00:10:01,410 --> 00:10:02,010
Of course.

160
00:10:03,590 --> 00:10:04,240
Come to my office

161
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:06,240
and take your schedule tomorrow morning.

162
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,140
Yes, Mr. Gu.

163
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,900
Congratulations, Cheng.

164
00:10:18,990 --> 00:10:19,800
Thank you.

165
00:10:24,310 --> 00:10:25,240
Order some meat.

166
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:34,200
Hello.

167
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,180
Please remove the listing for my apartment.

168
00:10:36,180 --> 00:10:37,390
I’m not selling it anymore.

169
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:37,990
Ms. Cheng,

170
00:10:38,290 --> 00:10:40,240
the location of your house is very popular.

171
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,150
Please reconsider.

172
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:42,560
No, thanks. Unlist it.

173
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:21,220
Dad, are you home?

174
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:24,240
Yes. Don't worry.

175
00:11:26,570 --> 00:11:27,430
By the way, dad,

176
00:11:27,430 --> 00:11:30,430
I’ve been transferred back to the Flight Department.

177
00:11:33,450 --> 00:11:33,910
Really?

178
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,940
That's great. Congratulations, daughter.

179
00:11:41,710 --> 00:11:42,520
Thanks, dad.

180
00:11:48,060 --> 00:11:49,630
This is from your mum.

181
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:07,760
Thank you.

182
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:15,080
Why are you smiling?

183
00:12:16,350 --> 00:12:16,950
Nothing.

184
00:12:17,450 --> 00:12:18,980
I'm watching a funny video.

185
00:12:19,010 --> 00:12:21,670
Don't look at your phone. It's bad for your eyes.

186
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,470
I know.

187
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:41,860
[Cheng Xiao’s flight schedule]

188
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:51,230
Am I going to fly 20 days in a month,

189
00:13:51,230 --> 00:13:52,210
on 60 flights?

190
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,690
Are you challenging my limits?

191
00:13:55,190 --> 00:13:56,920
I've evaluated this schedule.

192
00:13:58,050 --> 00:13:59,450
I can guarantee that

193
00:13:59,730 --> 00:14:01,120
you can sleep for ten hours every day.

194
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,390
The remaining two rest days

195
00:14:02,390 --> 00:14:03,980
are for you to do a safety report

196
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:05,910
and make a record of each flight.

197
00:14:06,090 --> 00:14:07,620
Don’t miss a single detail.

198
00:14:08,640 --> 00:14:09,300
No problem.

199
00:14:09,950 --> 00:14:11,010
As long as I can fly,

200
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:12,310
I can take anything.

201
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,400
I must make up for

202
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:14,600
all the time I've missed

203
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:17,200
while I was at the Ground Handling Department.

204
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:18,360
This time,

205
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,950
I’ve arranged different captains for you.

206
00:14:21,950 --> 00:14:24,150
Learn to adapt and cooperate with them.

207
00:14:25,710 --> 00:14:27,100
They are all your spies.

208
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:30,310
If you make any mistake,

209
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,720
you will be suspended immediately.

210
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:38,540
Cheng Xiao,

211
00:14:39,770 --> 00:14:41,400
I hope you can become a mature captain

212
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:42,460
as soon as possible

213
00:14:42,660 --> 00:14:44,060
to prove to everyone that

214
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:46,550
a female pilot can also be outstanding.

215
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,830
You were disapproving of me before,

216
00:14:53,830 --> 00:14:54,960
so I had to do my best.

217
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:58,240
Now that you think highly of me,

218
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:00,010
I want to do even better.

219
00:15:06,570 --> 00:15:07,370
President Xu.

220
00:15:15,310 --> 00:15:15,760
I know.

221
00:15:16,610 --> 00:15:17,740
I'll be right there.

222
00:15:32,380 --> 00:15:39,800
[Deputy Director of Flight Department]

223
00:15:41,620 --> 00:15:42,360
Let go!

224
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:51,650
What's going on?

225
00:15:52,610 --> 00:15:53,670
Hello, passenger.

226
00:16:00,330 --> 00:16:02,530
The PR department put in a lot of effort

227
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:04,490
to clarify the facts of the matter.

228
00:16:05,850 --> 00:16:07,580
The video was finally deleted.

229
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:10,250
But the bad impact it made

230
00:16:10,620 --> 00:16:11,900
cannot be retracted.

231
00:16:13,390 --> 00:16:14,710
I'm sorry, President Xu.

232
00:16:14,710 --> 00:16:16,790
I have caused trouble for the company.

233
00:16:16,790 --> 00:16:17,540
I mishandled

234
00:16:18,810 --> 00:16:19,850
this matter.

235
00:16:35,230 --> 00:16:38,070
Your position as Deputy Director of the Flight Department

236
00:16:38,070 --> 00:16:39,200
will be suspended.

237
00:16:40,370 --> 00:16:42,780
Your position as a pilot instructor remains

238
00:16:42,780 --> 00:16:44,180
and your flight schedule

239
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:45,770
will continue as usual.

240
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:51,010
Before the official internal investigation results come out,

241
00:16:51,170 --> 00:16:51,770
Mr. Jiang,

242
00:16:52,770 --> 00:16:55,500
you’ll take over all the work for now.

243
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:16,119
Brother-in-law.

244
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:17,420
Are you done with the meeting?

245
00:17:17,420 --> 00:17:18,349
Why are you here?

246
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:22,450
Mum made canned food for you.

247
00:17:22,470 --> 00:17:23,490
She knows you like it,

248
00:17:23,490 --> 00:17:24,319
so she asked me to bring them here for you

249
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:26,050
at the earliest possible time.

250
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,400
I'm so lucky.

251
00:17:29,790 --> 00:17:30,790
Brother-in-law,

252
00:17:31,490 --> 00:17:32,220
I heard

253
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:34,560
Mr. Gu's incident at the departure gate

254
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:36,130
has gone viral online.

255
00:17:37,580 --> 00:17:39,240
Everyone in the Flight Department

256
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,960
supports Mr. Gu unanimously.

257
00:17:48,230 --> 00:17:48,760
Get down.

258
00:17:50,050 --> 00:17:51,760
Hold yourself properly.

259
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:55,250
It's okay for you to listen to these things,

260
00:17:55,250 --> 00:17:57,380
but don't make statements about them.

261
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:01,970
President Xu just announced that

262
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:06,930
Gu Nanting will no longer be the Deputy Director of the Flight Department.

263
00:18:07,110 --> 00:18:07,570
Just...

264
00:18:08,330 --> 00:18:09,190
Just like that?

265
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:12,870
Don't be a busybody in the future.

266
00:18:17,390 --> 00:18:18,800
And my mother-in-law's cooking skills

267
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:20,040
are really amazing.

268
00:18:21,670 --> 00:18:22,030
Yes.

269
00:18:30,370 --> 00:18:32,380
[Master]

270
00:18:30,370 --> 00:18:32,380
[(5 messages) Master: Let's talk.]

271
00:18:35,350 --> 00:18:38,070
[Master]

272
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:22,140
Please open the door.

273
00:20:21,460 --> 00:20:24,520
There's no flight tomorrow and the day after tomorrow.

274
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:25,600
I've checked.

275
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:54,890
How is it?

276
00:20:55,850 --> 00:20:57,250
Do you feel more relaxed?

277
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:02,580
Deputy Director isn't a big deal.

278
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:06,570
You...

279
00:21:07,470 --> 00:21:09,400
are not suitable to be an official.

280
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:23,010
Why did you want to learn to fly?

281
00:21:25,600 --> 00:21:27,730
I don't think we've talked about this.

282
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:30,560
One time, I broached the topic

283
00:21:30,630 --> 00:21:31,840
but you didn't want to talk about it.

284
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:32,970
I never asked again.

285
00:21:35,950 --> 00:21:36,680
Afterwards,

286
00:21:37,070 --> 00:21:38,730
I found out about your family.

287
00:21:39,460 --> 00:21:40,390
I had my guesses.

288
00:21:43,380 --> 00:21:44,780
I'm more vulgar than you.

289
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:49,090
When I was young,

290
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:50,680
