578
00:41:56,390 --> 00:41:57,590
I just want to tell you

579
00:41:58,570 --> 00:42:00,170
to stop torturing yourself.

580
00:42:03,150 --> 00:42:05,280
I'm joining a half marathon next month.

581
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,340
I'm just training.

582
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:07,960
You're always like this.

583
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:09,360
You keep everything to yourself.

584
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:12,090
You'll get an internal injury if you keep this up.

585
00:42:12,310 --> 00:42:14,640
Have you been flying too little recently?

586
00:42:15,560 --> 00:42:16,680
I'm here to check in on you

587
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:18,410
after getting off my flight.

588
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:21,260
The flight data for every flight,

589
00:42:21,270 --> 00:42:22,490
from take off to landing,

590
00:42:22,490 --> 00:42:24,020
must be recorded down to the last detail.

591
00:42:24,020 --> 00:42:26,350
Send it to me for review after you're done.

592
00:42:27,680 --> 00:42:31,080
I was kind enough to check in on you, but you're so ungrateful.

593
00:42:32,270 --> 00:42:34,200
It's the biggest consolation to me

594
00:42:34,270 --> 00:42:35,370
if you can fly well.
